{{单双书号转换|'''我愛你'''}}（{{lang-en|"I Love You"}}）是由美國饒舌歌手[[香草冰|香草冰]]創作的饒舌歌曲。發行後於1990年登上[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百强单曲榜]]的第52位。<ref>"[http://www.allmusic.com/artist/vanilla-ice-mn0000262445/awards Awards] {{Wayback|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/vanilla-ice-mn0000262445/awards |date=20160513142703 }}", [[Allmusic|Allmusic]]. Retrieved 2013-04-27</ref>在英國音樂榜、德國和新西蘭上分別登上第45、65和30位<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/search/singles/I+Love+You|title=The Official Charts Company - I Love You by Vanilla Ice Search|date=2013-05-06|publisher=The Official Charts Company|accessdate=2020-11-07|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107151004/https://www.officialcharts.com/search/singles/i%20love%20you/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/Vanilla+Ice/single|title=Die ganze Musik im Internet: German Charts - Singles|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=2013-04-27|archive-date=2012-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011192731/http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/Vanilla+Ice/single|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://charts.nz/search.asp?search=Vanilla+Ice&cat=s|title=charts.nz - New Zealand charts portal|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=2013-04-27|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107151001/https://charts.nz/search.asp?search=Vanilla+Ice&cat=s|dead-url=no}}</ref>。與香草冰慣常的風格不同，〈我愛你〉是一首民謠，於1991年情人節發行<ref name="Huey">Huey, Steve "[http://www.allmusic.com/album/to-the-extreme-mw0000316695 ''To the Extreme'' Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/to-the-extreme-mw0000316695 |date=20190419124300 }}", [[Allmusic|Allmusic]]. Retrieved April 27, 2013</ref><ref name="Pioneer">"Johnson Grad Helps Rapper Vanilla Ice Flavor Valentine's Love Song", ''[[St._Paul_Pioneer_Press|St. Paul Pioneer Press]]'', February 8, 1991, p. 2C</ref>。該歌曲的[[音樂錄影帶|MV]]由[[麥可·貝|麥可·貝]]執導<ref name="Pioneer" />。

